message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and valued at $8000. Considering its exceptional quality and the benefits it provides, I believe we can reach an agreement that is mutually beneficial. I am proposing to sell it to you for $7500. This offer includes a comprehensive warranty and personalized support to ensure your satisfaction. Please let me know if this proposal meets your expectations or if you have any questions.
